SmartBird #1
"Pengmanii in hand is better than insurance."

Pengmanii is a combined NFT collection of Dr. Peng and Deokmanii, which provides membership benefits such as medical membership cultural activities and care for pets.
Pengmanii, who gives love, empathy, and healing, has the power to give good influence and positive energy.
Holders can experience healing in their present life by owning Pengmanii, and can receive various events and unique membership benefits.
Join us and enjoy your amazing membership with SmartBird NFT!
